snippet.textDisplay: It doesn't matter whether you sing at the back or at the front, people who have taste for quality music will always spot and support your talent, you have to be more careful while being a backing vocalist because the the singing of the lead singer is dependent on you, how you back the singer and you polish the lead singer's voice. So Rachel (and all other backing vocalists) have been a great asset to CokeStudio,without these superbly talented women CS wouldn't have been where it is today. Check "Neray Aah" on youtube to see Rachel's  singing capabilities, this song is nothing compared to that. A singer is a singer whether t the back or the front, so comments like finally Rachel is at the front don't make much sense. She has always been INCREDIBLE
